### 先下费用10.0的单
POST http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/place
Content-Type: application/json

{ "userId": 1, "scooterId": 1, "totalCost": 10.0 }

### 支付这一单 (变成 paid 状态)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/pay/1?cardNumber=666

### 申请延长 (再加 5.5 块钱)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/extend/1?extraCost=5.5

# 💡 最终检查：看数据库里 1 号订单的 total_cost 是不是变成了 15.5？